a>"},{"pid":"25440c6f66fe9a6695d248caaed8bb7c41225cd4","tid":1528461,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主無做錯到"},{"pid":"7a496420728bb65dc3cee89fb2ae4862acfb68e1","tid":1528461,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"著呢件衫去丢汽油彈會唔會令佢地人格分裂當場暴斃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7edb0a2f5ac1af8bfff520fd6f4775389729f9","tid":1528461,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"好，知道"},{"pid":"9fc3cd88f4d03091a224f4183d7159515c375829","tid":1528461,"uid":261900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15af2d366d547773370295811700f71a552779eb","tid":1528461,"uid":144306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"[代朋友po 佢冇連登ac]<br />\n我老母係專接大陸團嘅導遊，典型無腦on9藍絲嚟。呢排冇人落黎，佢就冇嘢做，日日喺到9叫俾人搞到佢冇嘢撈，睇親電視就係咁鬧，日日錄音同佢啲所謂同事喺到講示威者搞事冇建設，話示威者係曱甴，周圍搞破壞，話啲狗好辛苦，冇假放。呢兩個月同佢嘈過好多次都冇用，佢之前癲撚到拎咗枝支那旗同支持狗嘅襟章喺屋企到掛，我已經覺得佢痴撚咗線，點知佢今日帶咗兩個藍絲師奶上屋企，圍埋一齊對住部電視睇無綫直播喺到鬧鬧鬧，仲有一袋藍衫，我唔知佢哋會做啲咩嘢，但希望各位手足可以小心啲，就算整連儂牆都唔好自己一個去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tCFCDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tCFCDd.jpg&h=be19d496&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eReMybB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeReMybB.jpg&h=8a4a5ab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"錯grammar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03934ba19b22418f91778cb4f64fc1398182922f","tid":1528461,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-